Sam?

813
01:30:33,501 --> 01:30:34,835
Hey, Sam?

814
01:30:36,629 --> 01:30:37,964
You OK, buddy?

815
01:30:38,714 --> 01:30:40,382
Cavalry's here.

816
01:30:43,093 --> 01:30:44,637
