822
01:31:35,314 --> 01:31:38,360
Bag him up and we'll get started on
repairs to the harvester.

823
01:31:38,443 --> 01:31:40,112
Dwight, I'm going to need the...

824
01:31:48,975 --> 01:31:50,643
(ecstatic screaming)

